Go to build.gradle (Module : - app)
Inside android{} , just after testInstrumentationRunner , enable ViewBinding to true by :
buildFeatures{
  viewBinding true
}
Then synchronize the gradle file by clicking "Sync Now" at the top right
Then create an id , in your view of Xml file , which you want to access in your XActivity.kt
Now go to XActivity.kt
inside class XActivitydo the following modifications: //X is the name of the Activity

class XActivity : AppCompatActivity() {
    private lateinit var binding: ActivityXBinding
    override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)
        binding= ActivitXBinding.inflate(layoutInflater)
        setContentView(binding.root)
   
   Then happily access the id by using  binding.idname
   
   
   
   
   
